{"tid":1745448,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"假勞換真勞證物　男警盜竊罪成囚10個月","createTime":"2019-11-22T08:27:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T12:51:41.000Z","uid":34572,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"2595b77a7ad5cd2512b2da287f296e8c6ecf2435","tid":1745448,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:27:27.000Z","msg":"長沙灣警署一名男警前年處理一宗拾獲價值42萬港元勞力士手錶案件時，以一隻黑色錶面冒牌錶，偷龍轉鳳與淺藍色錶面真錶掉包，事後被揭發。涉案男警周合駿早前被裁定一項盜竊罪罪成，今日(22日)被判囚10個月。<br />\n辯方於判刑前再替被告呈上親友的求情信，信中皆讚揚被告為人正直、路不拾遺、樂於助人、樸素且不追求物質等，被告亦有向親友透露對此事件表示深切悔意，相信被告只是一時衝動及貪心犯事。辯方指被告自幼想成為一名警員，明白此事後已難如願，更嘗到鐵窗滋味，這已是對被告很大的懲罰及教訓，希望法庭輕判。<br />\n法官判刑時指被告犯案時乃是身為執法人員執行職務，情節較他為一般市民犯案時嚴重。惟考慮到案件不涉違反信託、被告有交還手錶令事主沒有損失，及法官接納他一時貪念犯事，致失去夢寐以求的職業等，遂將18個月量刑起點下調至10個月。法官並指被告一時貪念影響前途，令人十分惋惜，寄語被告出獄後能改過自新，在另一個崗位上服務社會。"},{"pid":"5dde64d0aef7996e502c10bd936aaf6963b22217","tid":1745448,"uid":126621,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:28:12.000Z","msg":"死黑警，無個好"},{"pid":"0fbba5340a1b0e9f53373267bb2f8d2350cb0afc","tid":1745448,"uid":34572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:28:20.000Z","msg":"延伸閱讀<br />\n<br />\n笑能死 唔見果隻42萬勞力士原來係假野黎<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/300992\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/300992</a>"},{"pid":"0e6d5f0c341812e2691bdfd4b08625a959160f85","tid":1745448,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:28:53.000Z","msg":"小氣"},{"pid":"7fec222a57e13308b9313355e5199c4e041c21ee","tid":1745448,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:28:55.000Z","msg":"25"},{"pid":"f38baa6e486dffcfaa4f68f7af7be2323d90d8b4","tid":1745448,"uid":230849,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:30:10.000Z","msg":"警察做咩唔賴佔中搞到有精神病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91ae312ceab3bc462f944b5399b88ed2b2fda178","tid":1745448,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:30:11.000Z","msg":"蓋清召喚"},{"pid":"d1ca84ac330ec89d5f3e5fa69e9c508f50e63162","tid":1745448,"uid":143435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:30:35.000Z","msg":"走得太前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a310e63e4e929c1c5ca2e5a898a19361d30a4c3","tid":1745448,"uid":255637,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:30:40.000Z","msg":"夢寐以求的職業<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n緊係啦 殺人又得 強姦又得 鍾意就拉d i banker  真係巴撚閉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21fba250cc1566864d0f4ce023573054b7ac8e34","tid":1745448,"uid":34572,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:31:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DTnE2te.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDTnE2te.gif&h=92747425&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"90058610fad73e59b8fde6cb420614fec68c9b2a","tid":1745448,"uid":58242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21fba250cc1566864d0f4ce023573054b7ac8e34","tid":1745448,"uid":34572,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:31:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DTnE2te.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDTnE2te.gif&h=92747425&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:31:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc29387b61bb013fc6eb00ca0cfb2e148e4f046a","tid":1745448,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:33:29.000Z","msg":"好唔抵<br />\n呢個連偷幾次<br />\n偷多成倍錢<br />\n仲要差人200萬先坐21個月<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190228/s00001/1551341554707/警隊指揮官盜86萬元現金證物-罪成判監21月\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190228%2Fs00001%2F1551341554707%2F%E8%AD%A6%E9%9A%8A%E6%8C%87%E6%8F%AE%E5%AE%98%E7%9B%9C86%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E7%8F%BE%E9%87%91%E8%AD%89%E7%89%A9-%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90%E5%88%A4%E7%9B%A321%E6%9C%88&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRyllA4V8ywhhxRXFDRWvztIyc%3D&h=30e47b33\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190228%2Fs00001%2F1551341554707%2F%E8%AD%A6%E9%9A%8A%E6%8C%87%E6%8F%AE%E5%AE%98%E7%9B%9C86%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E7%8F%BE%E9%87%91%E8%AD%89%E7%89%A9-%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90%E5%88%A4%E7%9B%A321%E6%9C%88&h=d072426b\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190228/s00001/1551341554707/警隊指揮官盜86萬元現金證物-罪成判監21月</a><br />\n警隊前助理分區指揮官（行政）劉永輝被指於前年在警局內偷竊屬於證物的現金，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">總值共86萬元</span></span>，款項其後全部用來賭波，至今他仍債台高築。劉永輝今於區域法院承認一項盜竊罪，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">被判入獄21個月</span></span>。劉求情稱，警隊是全世界最好的紀律部隊之一，他對其自私行為影響警隊形象深感抱歉。法官寄語他「不要放棄自己」，深信他出獄後可回饋社會。<br />\n<br />\n辯方求情指出，被告深感懊悔，事件摧毁其家人和事業，損失巨額的長俸，被告感到愧對家人，對人生失去希望，甚至企圖自殺，幸獲妻子救回。辯方呈上被告妻子的求情信，附帶一張由二人孩子繪畫家庭照的畫作，法官稱該畫作應「還給被告」，着他謹記賭博對家庭造成的後果。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n法官判刑稱，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">被告仍欠警察儲蓄互助社200萬元，過往又因賭博而欠下財務公司債項</span></span>，現時他準備申請破產。法官問及被告打算如何處理他的賭博習慣，辯方稱被告已沒有可賭博的資本，他出獄後能否找到工作也成疑問。<br />\n<br />\n法官指出，被告計劃盜竊的時間長達數月，並非單一事件，顯然經過預謀。法官續指出，雖然被告不是病態賭徒，但他責無旁貸，且身為經驗豐富的警務人員，必然深明犯罪後果。<br />\n<br />\n法官接納辯方呈上的30封求情信所指，被告是出色警察，貢獻良多，考慮因此減刑兩個月。法官寄語被告，他不是面對窮途末路，仍有強大的家庭和同事的支持，希望他出獄後回饋社會，成為更強和更好的人。<br />\n<br />\n案情指出，被告負責保管封存證物，駐守打鼓嶺警署。2017年10月至12月期間，有警員分別把人民幣7500元、31,290元和67萬元的款項交予被告封存在保險箱內，該67萬元分別放在67個防干擾封套內。<br />\n<br />\n2018年4月，一宗案件審訊時需要呈堂該些封套，但警員發現被告重整了封套，只餘34個，被告解釋這是為了騰出保險箱空間。同年6月，被告的上司檢視保險箱，發現上述的34個封套被開啟，內裏的金錢不翼而飛，另有5個封套內的金錢亦被取去。被告在警誡下承認盜取款項，且以道具鈔票充塞，留下真鈔票在表面，以此掩飾。"},{"pid":"415cbd991e769f93817f921daa3a127c1aa97f2e","tid":1745448,"uid":95499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:35:40.000Z","msg":"佢係咪色盲 黑色同淺藍差咁遠都諗住可以過到骨"},{"pid":"298d5872da448ed35f9e14905b1581c4e85801b8","tid":1745448,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:36:47.000Z","msg":"同場加映保安乜都冇偷要坐26個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑警係咪有特權？<br />\n黑警係咪大撚哂？<br />\n<br />\n取地氈藏匙入屋偷竊　保安員淆底乜都無偷囚26月<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190306/mobile/bkn-20190306124614716-0306_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190306%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190306124614716-0306_00822_001.html&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRyllA4V8ywhhxRXFDRWvztIyc%3D&h=e16b77bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190306/mobile/bkn-20190306124614716-0306_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"845bc05967f3ea1bdabf282ae82d38c673e9e2fd","tid":1745448,"uid":56230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:40:09.000Z","msg":"辯方於判刑前再替被告呈上親友的求情信，信中皆讚揚被告為人正直、<span style=\"color: red;\">路不拾遺</span>、樂於助人、樸素且<span style=\"color: red;\">不追求物質</span>等<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />路不拾遺但會偷 不追求物質但愛撈"},{"pid":"fe7423099285cd1524de045f89fd400ace2435d6","tid":1745448,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:59:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc0f85f55a63ecdada541bc6d542f2d797fcdcb7","tid":1745448,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T10:04:06.000Z","msg":"蓋"},{"pid":"23df5376bc0030ec7a81ecb5cab43a7901ce660f","tid":1745448,"uid":279401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T10:06:30.000Z","msg":"黑警！<br />\n1124一定要全民都投建制派<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1745329\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1745329</a>"},{"pid":"f91f4310771e0ff02aef9d1a7c8d7be2e2a2dddd","tid":1745448,"uid":339272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T10:18:44.000Z","msg":"警察職權過大，令警察利用職權犯案。<br />\n<br />\n警察身為執法者，但仍然犯案，<br />\n沒有守法意識，<br />\n政府沒有解決此矛盾。"},{"pid":"b98267d1d82191c220d3d563dee10d7c081798a8","tid":1745448,"uid":61604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:45:30.000Z","msg":"抵死"},{"pid":"b8ad06b37fb10ad279cbd2f21b42ed4683f2f0a7","tid":1745448,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90058610fad73e59b8fde6cb420614fec68c9b2a","tid":1745448,"uid":58242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21fba250cc1566864d0f4ce023573054b7ac8e34","tid":1745448,"uid":34572,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:31:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DTnE2te.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDTnE2te.gif&h=92747425&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:31:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:47:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"463f33fa4f0cd8d1608e94952227d38731e2eb1b","tid":1745448,"uid":45354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:47:33.000Z","msg":"小江"},{"pid":"37ecbec4d9a20e1298dab03ff44518d4e9921d83","tid":1745448,"uid":161263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:51:41.000Z","msg":"搞錯呀<br />\n狗犯法都要坐？世界變。"}]}